Package org.lockout

Class UserRequest

java.lang.Object
org.lockout.UserRequest
Direct Known Subclasses:
Getinfo, Login, Signup, Updates
public abstract class UserRequest extends Object
Final form of the incoming user request. First we deserialise incoming HTTP request to LambdaInput and finally to UserRequest to get all that ACTION (Action part and similar stuff properly deserialised from the LambdaInput.getBody() More of a conceptual intermediary than anything else. Login, Signup, Getinfo etc inherit fields from this class and implement their own methods or logic.
